# 🧠 SQL Learning Roadmap

A step-by-step guide to mastering SQL from beginner to advanced level.

📌 Check out the interactive mind map here:  
[SQL Roadmap Mind Map on MindMeister](https://www.mindmeister.com/app/map/2937557798?t=gEsd0gNKbd)

## 🗂️ Topics Covered
1. **Introduction**
2. **Query Data (SELECT)**
3. **Data Definition (DDL)**
4. **Data Manipulation (DML)**
5. **Filtering Data**
6. **Combining Data**
7. **Row-Level Functions**
8. **Aggregation & Analytical Functions**
9. **Advanced SQL Techniques**
10. **Performance Optimization**
11. **AI & SQL**
12. **SQL Projects**
